♪Sun and moon part, stars remain silent♪

25
00:01:18,010 --> 00:01:22,510
♪Through endless night, dawn paints its art♪

26
00:01:24,460 --> 00:01:29,980
=Serendipity=

27
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 5=

28
00:01:51,150 --> 00:01:53,000
Why is this pillow so hard?

29
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:54,640
Who has such a long neck,

30
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,350
sleeping on such a high pillow?

31
00:01:57,430 --> 00:01:58,270
The Yin Family...

32
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:01,920
Yin Shujun's indeed arrogant and domineering.

33
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:05,640
I still think this is strange.

34
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,790
It seems I have to take the initiative.

35
00:02:16,660 --> 00:02:19,500
(Ya House)

36
00:02:24,710 --> 00:02:25,710
I got it wrong.

37
00:02:27,310 --> 00:02:28,150
Brother,

38
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,310
you freak me out.

39
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:31,590
What are you doing here?

40
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,720
You...

41
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,400
How did you get in here?

42
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,870
You opened the door without asking

43
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:42,790
and didn't close the window before sleep.

44
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,960
You're so ignorant of prevention.

45
00:02:45,190 --> 00:02:46,870
How can I and our mother feel at ease?

46
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,520
You came in from the window.

47
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,910
Then who is knocking at the door?

48
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:59,030
Open the door.

49
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,280
Didn't you just say

50
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,800
I can't open the door without asking?

51
00:03:04,310 --> 00:03:06,030
I'm here.

52
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:09,120
It's me, Lady Mingshu.

53
00:03:11,430 --> 00:03:12,270
Mr. Song.

54
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,150
It's really you.

55
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,390
How come you are here?

56
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,690
I also came to the Yin Residence.

57
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,960
I just wanted to come see you.

58
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:23,520
She's so happy.

59
00:03:29,310 --> 00:03:30,470
For the next period of time,

60
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,890
I will stay at the Yin Residence.

61
00:03:34,030 --> 00:03:35,680
Did you come here to be a reading lady

62
00:03:35,740 --> 00:03:37,240
because you lack money to open a shop?

63
00:03:37,710 --> 00:03:38,550
That's right.

64
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,710
You have found a shop?

65
00:03:41,190 --> 00:03:42,590
What are the size and location?

66
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:44,470
Do you need me to look for another one?

67
00:03:45,310 --> 00:03:46,400
It's a coincidence.

68
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:47,800
That day we ran into Chenxin

69
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,430
on the street.

70
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,910
I drew a pattern for her.

71
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,960
Just then a shopkeeper saw it.

72
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,290
He had to return to his hometown,

73
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:55,750
so he transferred the shop to me.

74
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,920
That's very good.

75
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,910
You also know about her opening a shop?

76
00:04:01,470 --> 00:04:02,960
She has mentioned it to me.

77
00:04:03,590 --> 00:04:05,150
She has talent and will surely succeed.

78
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,430
It seems that only I, as her brother,

79
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,280
am unaware of this.

80
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:14,840
It's just a coincidence.

81
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:17,270
I wouldn't hide anything from you.

82
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,510
I know you love me.

83
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:22,430
I really like jewelry.

84
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:24,390
The more I understand,

85
00:04:24,510 --> 00:04:25,250
the more it helps

86
00:04:25,274 --> 00:04:27,174
with the recovery from amnesia.

87
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:29,920
(Amnesia?)

88
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:37,070
I don't want to rely only on you.

89
00:04:37,070 --> 00:04:38,920
I also want to have my own career

90
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,510
and do what I love.

91
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:43,160
Moreover, our mother has already agreed.

92
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,120
You're such a reasonable person.

93
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:50,630
I don't think you would refuse, right?

94
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:51,630
Since you say that,

95
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,120
if I don't agree,

96
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:55,260
it will make me seem unreasonable.

97
00:04:58,190 --> 00:04:59,510
You are the best.

98
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,870
Business is business.

99
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,680
Being a reading lady is a different matter.

100
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,510
Mr. Lu is right.

101
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,920
Although I'm happy that you can stay here,

102
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,680
that Lady Shujun

103
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,120
seems difficult to get along with.

104
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,650
It's better not to do this job.

105
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,750
I can lend you the money to open the shop.

106
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,000
Stop it!

107
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:22,040
I have already made up my mind.

108
00:05:22,310 --> 00:05:23,600
The Madam has already said,

109
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:25,430
if I can find the crux of Lady Shujun's

110
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,800
change in temperament,

111
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,560
there's a extra reward.

112
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:30,870
How could I miss such a good opportunity?

113
00:05:31,430 --> 00:05:33,190
Besides, aren't you also here?

114
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:36,360
I have to say this first.

115
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:39,040
If she bullies you,

116
00:05:39,190 --> 00:05:40,600
I will take you away at any time.

117
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:42,480
Am I someone who can be bullied?

118
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:44,430
Moreover, after class tomorrow,

119
00:05:44,630 --> 00:05:46,430
I also want to borrow your name

120
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,480
to show a bit.

121
00:05:58,190 --> 00:06:01,240
Last night I dreamed of my father.

122
00:06:01,590 --> 00:06:03,830
Since he died in battle ten years ago,

123
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:06,720
I haven't dreamed of him for a long time.

124
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,830
Don't be sad, Liangjun.

125
00:06:08,970 --> 00:06:10,360
The achievements of the second uncle

126
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,800
will be remembered by everyone.

127
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,560
(Liangjun's parents are both deceased.)

128
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,330
(Xianjun's father is addicted to alchemy)

129
00:06:21,330 --> 00:06:22,330
(and ignores everything.)

130
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,440
(Since the option for arranged marriages,)

131
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,480
(Shujun's personality has changed much,)

132
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,630
(frequently causing trouble.)

133
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,800
(Have the other two ladies)

134
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:33,680
(ever thought about taking her place?)

135
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,070
Your wrists are so slender.

136
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:45,460
Wearing this bracelet

137
00:06:45,484 --> 00:06:46,684
makes it even more exquisite.

138
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:50,480
This is newly made by Auntie.

139
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,430
Shujun thinks it's too heavy.

140
00:06:52,630 --> 00:06:54,480
Liangjun thinks gold and silver are vulgar.

141
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,680
So Auntie gave it to me.

142
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,120
I quite like it.

143
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,310
It's very suitable for you.

144
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:01,960
Lu Mingshu,

145
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,680
whose reading lady are you?

146
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,720
You go back first.

147
00:07:19,310 --> 00:07:20,150
Bro...

148
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,670
Who are you?

149
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,070
How dare you trespass here!

150
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:41,800
These two are Mr. Lu and Mr. Song.

151
00:07:42,410 --> 00:07:43,720
The Master has given instructions,

152
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,920
from today onwards,

153
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:47,830
Mr. Lu will temporarily teach literature,

154
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:50,600
while Mr. Song'll teach you to play the Qin.

155
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,630
Mr. Lu, I'll teach the Qin in the next class.

156
00:08:05,950 --> 00:08:06,870
I have nothing to do,

157
00:08:06,894 --> 00:08:08,706
so I will stay here to listen to your class.

158
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,470
Okay.

159
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,450
Isn't that Mr. Song

160
00:08:12,474 --> 00:08:13,786
from the Duke of the State?

161
00:08:14,310 --> 00:08:15,360
The cousin of Prince Rui.

162
00:08:15,830 --> 00:08:18,070
He actually came in person to teach us.

163
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:20,070
Liangjun, don't be too excited.

164
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:21,120
How to stay calm?

165
00:08:21,430 --> 00:08:22,680
What a rare opportunity!

166
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,680
And that Mr. Lu as well.

167
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:27,560
He is also elegant and outstanding.

168
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:29,630
But he looks somewhat aloof.

169
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:36,420
(Runwen Study)

170
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:39,600
We gather fern, which springs up here.

171
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:44,440
Why not return, now ends the year?

172
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,270
A restaurant in the east of the city

173
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,490
has delicious flavors.

174
00:09:08,950 --> 00:09:10,240
How about I treat you and Mr. Lu

175
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,240
to a meal another day?

176
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,150
Now ends the year?

177
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:21,080
The poem A Homesick Warrior we learned today

178
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:23,270
not only has the heroism of soldiers,

179
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,600
but also the gentle sentiment
of homesickness.

180
00:09:26,630 --> 00:09:28,480
Why not ask Mr. Song

181
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,390
to play the Qin for us?

182
00:09:31,390 --> 00:09:32,700
It will definitely add more charm.

183
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,040
Great!

184
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:35,630
Great!

185
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:22,240
One is graceful and handsome, warm as spring,

186
00:10:22,630 --> 00:10:24,100
while the other is steady and poised,

187
00:10:24,124 --> 00:10:25,306
like a jade tree in the wind.

188
00:10:26,030 --> 00:10:27,630
I really don't know which one to look at.

189
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:31,600
A gentleman of integrity,
polished and refined.

190
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,030
It probably refers to someone like Mr. Lu.

191
00:10:41,460 --> 00:10:45,140
(Poetry, Books, Rites, and Music)

192
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:49,940
(Runwen Study)

193
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,550
Lady Shujun, please wait a moment.

194
00:11:05,720 --> 00:11:07,030
What is your explanation for this?

195
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:10,120
I don't want to embarrass you.

196
00:11:10,510 --> 00:11:11,790
But I have always been like this.

197
00:11:12,550 --> 00:11:13,870
If I wrote to you,

198
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:16,240
wouldn't it be unfair to my previous teacher?

199
00:11:17,910 --> 00:11:19,670
I've heard Grand Tutor Yin and Censor Yin

200
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,430
are strict with their children.

201
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,120
I don't know how they will think

202
00:11:25,350 --> 00:11:26,700
of being disrespectful to teachers.

203
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:31,750
If you don't submit homework,

204
00:11:32,630 --> 00:11:34,200
I'm afraid you can't go out

205
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:36,200
during monthly breaks.

206
00:11:37,390 --> 00:11:38,600
During my teaching period,

207
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,790
I will definitely pay more attention to you

208
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,090
and promptly report

209
00:11:43,114 --> 00:11:44,376
your whereabouts to Censor Yin,

210
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,790
to fulfill the duty of guidance.

211
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:51,510
You are threatening me?

212
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,960
He has always been a man of his word.

213
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,960
I hope you will think carefully.

214
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,080
What do you want?

215
00:12:00,340 --> 00:12:01,650
Hit you with a ferule three times,

216
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,150
as a punishment.

217
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:04,110
You sauce!

218
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,680
My Lady,

219
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:10,240
if he reports to the Master every day,

220
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:11,320
you'll not have peaceful days

221
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:13,150
in the future.

222
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:18,990
Okay.

223
00:12:19,910 --> 00:12:20,750
Then go ahead.

224
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,870
Although you are my student,

225
00:12:23,400 --> 00:12:24,550
you're a woman and I'm a man.

226
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,280
Then

227
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,870
let the reading lady take on the task.

228
00:12:35,030 --> 00:12:36,750
The reading lady has a duty to supervise.

229
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,670
It is more suitable for her to do it.

230
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:42,120
Lady Shujun.

231
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:48,000
Ready?

232
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:55,720
I thought of another way to punish.

233
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,840
I wonder if you would agree.

234
00:12:58,790 --> 00:13:00,150
Lady Shujun

235
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:01,840
is not focused on studies.

236
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:04,200
She must be affected by other matters.

237
00:13:04,630 --> 00:13:06,550
I want to check her residence

238
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:08,550
and clear out all those things

239
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:09,960
that are detrimental to her studies.

240
00:13:10,150 --> 00:13:11,750
The Madam will definitely agree to it.

241
00:13:13,390 --> 00:13:14,510
Lu Mingshu, do you dare?

242
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,350
I agree.

243
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,270
There is one more thing to inform you.

244
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:22,120
I am Lady Mingshu's brother.

245
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:24,720
You are siblings?

246
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,870
So you are taking advantage of it

247
00:13:28,870 --> 00:13:29,830
to deliberately fool me.

248
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,680
You are right.

249
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:32,840
How you treat my sister

250
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,790
is how I will

251
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,320
treat you.

252
00:13:37,630 --> 00:13:38,750
If you do not accept it,

253
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,630
you can report to Censor Yin at any time.

254
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,840
I may lack power,

255
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,750
but I am very protective.

256
00:13:45,000 --> 00:13:46,750
If anyone dares to disrespect my sister,

257
00:13:47,150 --> 00:13:47,990
I

258
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:49,910
will certainly not let it go easily.

259
00:13:58,840 --> 00:13:59,680
Shuangyan.

260
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,960
You wait outside first.

261
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:08,480
Lady Shujun, your room is truly

262
00:14:10,120 --> 00:14:11,550
magnificent and splendid.

263
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,270
You really never see the world.

264
00:14:16,630 --> 00:14:19,630
Are you taking advantage of your brother

265
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,360
to broaden your horizons at my place?

266
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,320
You guessed right.

267
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,480
I just want to see

268
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:26,960
what the boudoir of a young lady is like.

269
00:14:33,820 --> 00:14:35,740
(The Book of Songs)

270
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,600
Who told you to touch it?

271
00:14:38,870 --> 00:14:39,720
So what if I touch it?

272
00:14:40,270 --> 00:14:41,790
If you don't want to, go ask the Madam.

273
00:14:41,910 --> 00:14:43,240
Let's see what she will say.

274
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:54,350
You...!

275
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:57,180
(Shujun)

276
00:14:57,630 --> 00:14:59,510
This seal must belong to you, right?

277
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:00,350
Handwritten by you?

278
00:15:02,790 --> 00:15:04,240
If you break my stuff,

279
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,270
I guarantee that no one can save you.

280
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,560
Greetings, Madam.

281
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:30,870
What a refined embroidery!

