00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,320
Who is this mandarin duck embroidered for?

283
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:35,030
Why not let the Madam know?

284
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,080
Give it to me!

285
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:38,250
Tell me first who it's embroidered for.

286
00:15:38,670 --> 00:15:39,670
Why should I tell you?

287
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:42,020
If you don't, then let me keep it.

288
00:15:42,380 --> 00:15:43,240
I...

289
00:15:43,360 --> 00:15:44,390
Give it to me!

290
00:15:44,390 --> 00:15:45,360
I won't.

291
00:15:45,360 --> 00:15:46,390
I told you to tell me.

292
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:47,240
Why are they fighting?

293
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,150
Why should I tell you?

294
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:49,550
- Give it back.
- Tell me.

295
00:15:49,550 --> 00:15:50,480
Why are you fighting?

296
00:15:50,780 --> 00:15:51,620
You...

297
00:15:51,630 --> 00:15:53,030
- I won't.
- Give it back to me!

298
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,240
- Tell me.
- They're fighting.

299
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:56,480
- Tell the Madam?
- Don't go too far.

300
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:57,870
- Not yet.
- Lady Shujun.

301
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:00,510
- Why are you so angry?
- Lu Mingshu!

302
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:01,800
Give it to me, Lu Mingshu!

303
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,920
Lady Shujun, please tell me.

304
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,000
Give it back to me!

305
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:05,550
Alright, alright, alright.

306
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:08,240
I'm done with the fuss today.

307
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,080
I'm tired.

308
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,200
Here you are.

309
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:14,630
Get lost!

310
00:16:14,750 --> 00:16:15,910
Go, hurry up,

311
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:18,870
Lu Mingshu,

312
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:20,480
how dare you act like this today.

313
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,610
No one can keep you here.

314
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:25,240
You always say

315
00:16:25,240 --> 00:16:26,840
the same clichés,

316
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:29,200
like asking me to get out of here.

317
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,200
I've heard enough.

318
00:16:31,200 --> 00:16:32,440
Can you say something different?

319
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,030
You put in a lot of effort to pretend.

320
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:36,120
Are you tired?

321
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:43,870
What did you say?

322
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:48,240
The details here can't deceive anyone.

323
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:49,140
Lady Shujun,

324
00:16:49,164 --> 00:16:51,164
your calligraphy and painting are impressive

325
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:53,510
and have quite a study on the Book of Songs.

326
00:16:53,910 --> 00:16:55,510
But you always go against the teacher.

327
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:56,960
If you don't pretend, what is it?

328
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:01,000
What's wrong with that?

329
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,550
I am very happy to see the teacher angry.

330
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:05,440
I want everyone to fear me.

331
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,080
Lu Mingshu,

332
00:17:07,510 --> 00:17:08,880
don't you want a reward?

333
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,110
You wish!

334
00:17:10,680 --> 00:17:12,240
I will definitely drive you out.

335
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:14,030
Wishful thinking.

336
00:17:14,440 --> 00:17:16,030
You are about to marry the Prince Rui.

337
00:17:16,030 --> 00:17:18,400
Do you think the Madam will let you go?

338
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:20,960
Without me, there are still others.

339
00:17:24,310 --> 00:17:26,200
You better coexist peacefully with me

340
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:28,310
and live in harmony until you get engaged.

341
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:35,110
In your dream.

342
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,350
That's fine.

343
00:17:37,680 --> 00:17:39,070
Let's continue the fight like this.

344
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:42,240
You keep putting obstacles in my way.

345
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:43,410
My brother and I

346
00:17:43,434 --> 00:17:44,934
will pay you back in kind.

347
00:17:45,310 --> 00:17:48,030
This day will definitely be amazing

348
00:17:48,270 --> 00:17:49,400
and absolutely wonderful.

349
00:17:49,510 --> 00:17:50,350
You!

350
00:17:53,590 --> 00:17:54,590
I'll have the tea.

351
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:55,430
I'm leaving now.

352
00:17:55,430 --> 00:17:57,310
(Zhongrui House)

353
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:58,150
Lu Mingshu,

354
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,720
you will pay for what

355
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,680
you've done today.

356
00:18:04,590 --> 00:18:05,430
My Lady.

357
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:07,880
Nanny, this is specially made for you.

358
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,960
- You can share the rest.
- So beautiful!

359
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,240
I made all of them by hand.

360
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:14,240
- Mingshu, you are so skillful.
- Take a look.

361
00:18:15,510 --> 00:18:17,440
If you have any jewelry that needs repair,

362
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:18,440
you can come to me.

363
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,240
I guarantee it will look better than before.

364
00:18:20,240 --> 00:18:21,110
Really?

365
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,200
I'll open a jewelry shop

366
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,510
in a while.

367
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:24,720
If you are free,

368
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:25,830
you can come and support me.

369
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:27,200
- Sure.
- Sure.

370
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,830
I would like to ask you

371
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,790
for a favor.

372
00:18:31,790 --> 00:18:32,680
Just say it.

373
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,240
Lady Mingshu, just feel free to tell us.

374
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,240
I have heard some rumors about Lady Shujun.

375
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,160
As her reading lady,

376
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,440
I want to know something,

377
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,440
so I can get prepared.

378
00:18:43,880 --> 00:18:44,830
Listen to me,

379
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:46,550
Lady Shujun used to have a cat,

380
00:18:46,550 --> 00:18:48,640
but later I don't know why it died.

381
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,880
Have you seen anything?

382
00:18:53,030 --> 00:18:53,870
Mother.

383
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:56,240
For Mingshu?

384
00:18:56,680 --> 00:18:57,520
Right.

385
00:18:58,350 --> 00:18:59,640
The pillow there is a bit high.

386
00:19:00,240 --> 00:19:01,920
I think she isn't used to sleeping on it.

387
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:05,750
She probably won't be back for a while.

388
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:07,160
Bring her more clothes.

389
00:19:08,050 --> 00:19:08,990
I've already taken them.

390
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:12,640
When I heard

391
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,400
she wants to open a jewelry shop,

392
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:15,880
I was also surprised.

393
00:19:16,920 --> 00:19:18,350
Even if she forgot herself,

394
00:19:19,110 --> 00:19:20,960
she never forgot her love for jewelry.

395
00:19:21,550 --> 00:19:22,880
I think she opened a shop

396
00:19:23,030 --> 00:19:25,160
not simply to make some money,

397
00:19:25,680 --> 00:19:27,440
but also to gradually find herself again.

398
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:30,720
I used to think

399
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:32,480
she was just a pretty smart delicate lady,

400
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:33,720
but it seems now

401
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:36,160
she has her own realm in her heart,

402
00:19:36,920 --> 00:19:38,400
much wider than I thought.

403
00:19:38,830 --> 00:19:40,640
You didn't understand her at all before.

404
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:42,640
You always avoided her.

405
00:19:43,510 --> 00:19:44,510
She is such a good child

406
00:19:44,510 --> 00:19:46,400
all the time.

407
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:49,590
I'm leaving, mother.

408
00:20:01,180 --> 00:20:04,580
(Residence of Duke of the State)

409
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:11,580
(Xu Ruoyi)

410
00:20:12,020 --> 00:20:14,100
(Song Mingjie)

411
00:20:19,660 --> 00:20:22,900
(Auspicious and Elegant)

412
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,270
I had already told you

413
00:20:24,590 --> 00:20:25,920
to come back early.

414
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:28,250
Mr. Fang specially came here

415
00:20:28,250 --> 00:20:29,610
to give you guidance on discourse.

416
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:31,030
What a rare opportunity!

417
00:20:31,650 --> 00:20:32,640
Why didn't you come back?

418
00:20:33,100 --> 00:20:34,140
I know my mistake, Father.

419
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,030
I ask you to punish me.

420
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,160
Don't get yourself worked up.

421
00:20:39,030 --> 00:20:40,960
I only have you as my son.

422
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:43,350
The future glory of our family

423
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:44,680
relies on you.

424
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:47,060
The exam is coming soon.

425
00:20:47,500 --> 00:20:49,130
But you have been neglecting your studies.

426
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:49,980
Are you being true

427
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:51,440
to your ancestors by doing this?

428
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:53,880
I remember your teachings.

429
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:56,720
Yesterday,

430
00:20:57,070 --> 00:20:58,440
I helped the cousin with something.

431
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:00,040
I hope you can be forgiving.

432
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:01,590
Prince Rui?

433
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,830
You are working for Prince Rui.

434
00:21:06,960 --> 00:21:08,480
I should be supportive.

435
00:21:09,000 --> 00:21:09,840
But

436
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,930
the spring exam is approaching,

437
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:14,400
do not neglect your studies.

438
00:21:15,070 --> 00:21:15,960
Father, rest assured.

439
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:18,200
I do not dare to have any slackness.

440
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,920
Return home before the hour of You.

441
00:21:24,044 --> 00:21:24,946
This is a family rule.

442
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,590
You have violated the family rule.

443
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:28,200
What should you do?

444
00:21:28,830 --> 00:21:30,180
I will kneel in the ancestral hall

445
00:21:30,204 --> 00:21:30,786
for an hour

446
00:21:31,510 --> 00:21:32,720
and repent to the ancestors.

447
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:34,790
However, the matter of Prince Rui

448
00:21:34,814 --> 00:21:35,926
concerns the Yin Family.

449
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,240
After I finish kneeling,

450
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,590
I may still have to leave.

451
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,640
If necessary, I will stay overnight there.

452
00:21:42,270 --> 00:21:43,160
Please approve it.

453
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:50,110
No next time.

454
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:52,830
Thank you, father.

455
00:21:55,070 --> 00:21:55,910
Sir.

456
00:21:56,880 --> 00:21:57,720
Slow down.

457
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:07,720
Here.

458
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:09,440
Calm down.

459
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:14,760
You

460
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:18,270
are being too harsh on Qingzhao.

461
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,590
No matter how minor his mistake is,

462
00:22:20,614 --> 00:22:22,176
you punish him severely without mercy.

463
00:22:22,200 --> 00:22:24,790
If you don't care, I care.

464
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:27,750
Confucius said,

465
00:22:28,310 --> 00:22:30,000
less is nature,

466
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:32,160
habit is like nature.

467
00:22:33,270 --> 00:22:34,240
We must never slack off

468
00:22:34,830 --> 00:22:36,510
in educating children.

469
00:22:36,640 --> 00:22:38,310
Besides, you and I only have one son.

470
00:22:38,510 --> 00:22:39,680
Not even a bit...

471
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:42,030
not even the slightest mistake.

472
00:22:43,550 --> 00:22:45,000
Look at him now.

473
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:46,450
He is successful in his studies,

474
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:48,200
dignified and generous.

475
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,830
Isn't this my achievement?

476
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,830
If you could just praise him in person,

477
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:55,920
I'm not that difficult to deal with.

478
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,320
Sir...

479
00:23:06,440 --> 00:23:07,440
Sir, are you okay?

480
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:09,720
It's just kneeling for an hour.

481
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,760
It's okay.

482
00:23:12,350 --> 00:23:13,750
You know the Master is strict,

483
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:15,240
yet you still came back late

484
00:23:15,480 --> 00:23:16,480
and get punished.

485
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:17,830
Is it worth it?

486
00:23:18,790 --> 00:23:19,630
You don't understand.

487
00:23:21,750 --> 00:23:22,880
Who knows

488
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:24,070
it's for Prince Rui

489
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:26,030
or for Lady Lu?

490
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:28,310
Of course I am wholeheartedly

491
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,070
working for my cousin.

492
00:23:46,110 --> 00:23:46,950
It's so dirty.

493
00:23:47,100 --> 00:23:47,950
Take it.

494
00:23:48,070 --> 00:23:48,910
Yes.

495
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,070
Then let's throw it out.

496
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:02,240
Such a small cat doesn't eat or drink.

497
00:24:02,680 --> 00:24:03,720
It will starve to death.

498
00:24:05,640 --> 00:24:06,480
Keep it.

499
00:24:09,790 --> 00:24:12,270
Don't you dislike cats?

500
00:24:13,400 --> 00:24:15,070
Recently, my grandfather has been bedridden.

501
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,640
I'll consider it as doing good deeds.

502
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:18,920
Take good care of it.

503
00:24:19,310 --> 00:24:20,310
Don't let it bother me.

504
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,680
What do you want, Mother?

505
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,040
Shujun,

506
00:24:36,250 --> 00:24:37,860
the day after tomorrow, Noble Consort Hua

507
00:24:37,864 --> 00:24:38,940
will send someone to arrange

508
00:24:38,940 --> 00:24:40,290
a marriage for you with Prince Rui.

509
00:24:40,290 --> 00:24:41,440
Before this,

510
00:24:41,550 --> 00:24:43,000
don't make any trouble.

511
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:46,790
A marriage alliance is so important.

512
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,550
Why does it have to fall on me?

513
00:24:50,030 --> 00:24:50,920
What nonsense?

514
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:53,510
Have you ever asked for my opinion?

515
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:55,640
How did you know I wanted to marry him?

516
00:24:56,270 --> 00:24:57,550
Marriage is a matter

517
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:59,830
decided by the parents.

518
00:25:00,400 --> 00:25:02,160
Plus, you're the legitimate eldest daughter,

519
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:04,550
in any aspect of consideration,

520
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,030
you cannot avoid it.

521
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:08,830
In the capital,

522
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,640
except the princesses,

523
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:13,160
which lady can compare to you?

524
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:15,160
You are meant to be someone extraordinary.

525
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,440
Marrying into the royal family

526
00:25:16,464 --> 00:25:17,726
is your best destination.

527
00:25:18,750 --> 00:25:19,590
Alright.

528
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:22,440
Let the past be the past.

529
00:25:22,750 --> 00:25:24,160
As long as you're willing to change,

530
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:25,550
it's not too late for everything.

531
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:29,920
I really don't care about it.

532
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:33,170
Do you really want to force me like this?

533
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,110
We're not forcing you.

534
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:37,160
This is for your own good.

535
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:42,720
You...

536
00:25:53,310 --> 00:25:54,150
My Lady,

537
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:57,000
the marriage alliance can't be changed.

538
00:25:57,400 --> 00:26:00,000
You have let go of some things.

539
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,720
Who says it cannot be changed?

540
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,960
Things depend on human effort.

541
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:31,550
You deliver this thing to my third uncle.

542
00:26:31,750 --> 00:26:33,750
Also, bring back some things for me.

543
00:26:48,260 --> 00:26:50,660
(Runwen Study)

544
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:41,720
Mr. Song,

545
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:43,790
what a wonderful skill!

546
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:45,880
In tomorrow's class,

547
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:48,000
those ladies will surely be captivated again.

548
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,270
Thank you for praising me.

549
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:50,950
Lady Mingshu,

550
00:27:51,310 --> 00:27:52,440
do you want to play?

551
00:27:58,400 --> 00:27:59,310
I should be

552
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,640
unable to play.

553
00:28:01,480 --> 00:28:02,560
I forgot many things

554
00:28:02,584 --> 00:28:03,884
due to amnesia.

555
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:07,880
I remember you mentioning this before.

556
00:28:08,510 --> 00:28:09,440
I dare not ask much.

557
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,640
What is going on?

558
00:28:13,110 --> 00:28:13,960
It's no big deal.

559
00:28:14,300 --> 00:28:15,490
Caused by falling off a cliff.

560
00:28:16,990 --> 00:28:17,840
Life is not affected.

561
00:28:19,400 --> 00:28:20,400
If you have ever learnt,

562
00:28:21,410 --> 00:28:22,480
the skills you have learned

563
00:28:22,720 --> 00:28:24,000
will naturally be remembered.

564
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:25,440
Give it a try.

565
00:28:56,140 --> 00:28:59,900
(Runwen Study)

