00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:20,030
Brother,

570
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:22,680
I always make mistakes when I play the Qin.

571
00:29:23,070 --> 00:29:24,920
I wonder if you could give me some guidance.

572
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:29,160
I will play it for you.

573
00:29:48,460 --> 00:29:50,860
(Phoenix Seeking His Mate)

574
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:58,240
It's always wrong right here.

575
00:29:58,720 --> 00:30:00,200
I don't know where the problem lies.

576
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:04,070
I'm not very familiar with this piece either.

577
00:30:04,350 --> 00:30:05,190
Sorry,

578
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,350
I can't teach you.

579
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,000
(It turns out she was sincerely)

580
00:30:18,024 --> 00:30:19,346
(seeking my advice at that time,)

581
00:30:20,270 --> 00:30:21,440
(but I misunderstood her.)

582
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:27,420
(Runwen Study)

583
00:30:27,830 --> 00:30:28,990
If you want to learn the Qin,

584
00:30:29,480 --> 00:30:30,510
I can teach you too.

585
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,080
Brother.

586
00:30:32,640 --> 00:30:33,480
Brother.

587
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:34,980
Mr. Lu, don't be anxious.

588
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:36,770
Lady Mingshu understands immediately.

589
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:38,290
Maybe she has already figured it out.

590
00:30:39,440 --> 00:30:40,310
Yeah, brother,

591
00:30:40,310 --> 00:30:41,440
you go about your business.

592
00:30:41,590 --> 00:30:42,750
Mr. Song teaches ME very well.

593
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,160
I can learn from him.

594
00:30:47,240 --> 00:30:48,080
Take a break.

595
00:30:48,820 --> 00:30:49,950
I have something to tell you.

596
00:30:53,690 --> 00:30:54,550
Sorry to disturb you.

597
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:00,310
Isn't this my pillow?

598
00:31:00,620 --> 00:31:02,200
(Runwen Study)
I brought it specially for you.

599
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:04,790
You are so considerate, brother.

600
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:05,720
Brother,

601
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,240
is this a blessing of being your sister?

602
00:31:07,590 --> 00:31:09,030
Which lady will be so fortunate

603
00:31:09,030 --> 00:31:09,960
to marry you

604
00:31:09,960 --> 00:31:11,070
in the future?

605
00:31:11,100 --> 00:31:12,220
Stop. Or give it back to me.

606
00:31:12,350 --> 00:31:14,220
- Pure water produces lotus flowers.
- This is for me.

607
00:31:14,220 --> 00:31:15,510
Natural and unadorned.

608
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:17,640
Mr. Lu has such a sister,

609
00:31:18,750 --> 00:31:19,920
truly enviable to others.

610
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:22,660
(Harmony with Light and Dust)

611
00:31:22,680 --> 00:31:23,520
By the way, brother,

612
00:31:24,110 --> 00:31:25,400
what brings you to me today?

613
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:28,640
Did you find anything

614
00:31:28,700 --> 00:31:29,840
at Lady Shujun's place today?

615
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:32,350
How to put it?

616
00:31:32,590 --> 00:31:33,850
Lady Shujun is skilled

617
00:31:33,874 --> 00:31:35,156
in literature and painting.

618
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,350
She is also good at embroidery.

619
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:39,100
She must be carefully raised

620
00:31:39,124 --> 00:31:40,096
by the Yin Family.

621
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,030
I really can't understand

622
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:43,650
why her temperament would suddenly change.

623
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:45,240
Embroidery?

624
00:31:47,400 --> 00:31:48,230
I also heard

625
00:31:48,254 --> 00:31:50,154
she won't go to the Runwen Study tomorrow,

626
00:31:50,160 --> 00:31:51,330
to meet a distinguished guest.

627
00:31:54,480 --> 00:31:55,320
Brother,

628
00:31:55,360 --> 00:31:56,790
I didn't expect I could play the Qin.

629
00:31:56,790 --> 00:31:58,110
Did you teach me before?

630
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:02,750
At that time, you really

631
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:05,880
enjoyed listening to me play the Qin.

632
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,070
If you want to learn again,

633
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,990
I will definitely teach you well.

634
00:32:11,900 --> 00:32:13,160
- Only I can teach you.
- I...

635
00:32:23,220 --> 00:32:24,820
(Baopu House)

636
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:26,070
What brings you here, Shuangyan?

637
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:27,790
My lady has just received

638
00:32:27,790 --> 00:32:29,400
this excellent pear incense

639
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:31,110
and asked me to bring it here.

640
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:33,030
The master is currently alchemizing.

641
00:32:33,030 --> 00:32:34,000
He doesn't see anyone.

642
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,840
Leave it to me.

643
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:38,110
(Shuangyan)
This incense is very precious.

644
00:32:38,200 --> 00:32:39,470
Please make sure to keep it safe.

645
00:32:39,830 --> 00:32:40,670
Yes.

646
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,240
My Lady,

647
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,400
are you sure about this?

648
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:57,800
Once this proposal falls into

649
00:32:57,800 --> 00:32:58,990
the hands of Imperial Astronomer,

650
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,400
then there will be no turning back.

651
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,720
You know I don't want to marry Prince Rui.

652
00:33:03,830 --> 00:33:05,070
What's there to hesitate about?

653
00:33:06,000 --> 00:33:08,240
If this matter is discovered,

654
00:33:08,830 --> 00:33:10,350
will it bring any trouble?

655
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,680
What trouble could there be?

656
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:14,520
Here.

657
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,480
My mother

658
00:33:18,640 --> 00:33:20,110
likes to put the most valuable things

659
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,350
on the top of the cabinet by the east door.

660
00:33:22,510 --> 00:33:23,350
You remember it?

661
00:33:23,830 --> 00:33:25,200
Yes, My Lady.

662
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:26,880
I know what to do.

663
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,240
Go ahead.

664
00:33:28,540 --> 00:33:33,060
(Zhongrui House)

665
00:33:36,550 --> 00:33:37,640
Greetings, Noble Eunuch,

666
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,000
Mr. Song.

667
00:33:40,400 --> 00:33:43,240
Noble Consort Hua is concerned about you

668
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,590
and asked me to send her regards to you.

669
00:33:45,920 --> 00:33:47,390
Please make sure to visit the palace

670
00:33:47,414 --> 00:33:48,396
when you have the time.

671
00:33:48,900 --> 00:33:50,290
I'm deeply grateful to her kindness.

672
00:33:50,290 --> 00:33:51,400
I feel immensely honored.

673
00:33:51,750 --> 00:33:53,550
It's just that Her Highness is very busy,

674
00:33:53,550 --> 00:33:55,200
I dare not disturb her carelessly.

675
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,920
I only wish for the marriage to be settled.

676
00:33:58,430 --> 00:34:00,110
I shall certainly go pay my respects to her

677
00:34:00,270 --> 00:34:01,480
and get a glimpse of her grace.

678
00:34:06,400 --> 00:34:08,440
Lady Shujun is generous and courteous.

679
00:34:08,590 --> 00:34:10,360
No wonder Her Highness likes you.

680
00:34:11,070 --> 00:34:12,280
Since we've already met,

681
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:14,960
I should return to the palace to report.

682
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:27,080
My daughter's name and birthday

683
00:34:27,080 --> 00:34:28,800
(Lady Yin's Marriage Proposal)
are all recorded inside.

684
00:34:28,810 --> 00:34:29,640
Here.

685
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:38,630
Please wait for good news.

686
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:40,880
Thank you very much.

687
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:14,670
Help!

688
00:35:16,670 --> 00:35:17,760
Help!

689
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:18,840
Help!

690
00:35:20,030 --> 00:35:20,960
Help!

691
00:35:21,140 --> 00:35:23,300
(Huaixiu Pavilion)
Help!

692
00:35:23,300 --> 00:35:24,380
Someone fell into the water.

693
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,960
- Someone fell into the water.
- Oh no!

694
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:27,800
Come on.

695
00:35:27,800 --> 00:35:28,880
Come on! Help!

696
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:29,720
No way.

697
00:35:30,470 --> 00:35:31,470
Right over there.

698
00:35:42,590 --> 00:35:43,430
Lady Mingshu.

699
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,200
Mr. Lu.

700
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:50,840
Mr. Lu, take her back to the room first.

701
00:35:51,150 --> 00:35:52,440
Please pay attention

702
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:53,580
to whether it is an accident

703
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:54,710
or a man-made incident.

704
00:35:55,030 --> 00:35:55,870
Understood.

705
00:36:07,070 --> 00:36:09,760
Isn't that the reading lady?

706
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,700
Could it be because

707
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:13,370
she had a fight with Lady Shujun last time,

708
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:15,000
and Lady Shujun wanted to punish her

709
00:36:15,360 --> 00:36:16,670
out of anger?

710
00:36:17,880 --> 00:36:19,110
What nonsense are you saying?

711
00:36:24,440 --> 00:36:25,280
Liangjun,

712
00:36:26,710 --> 00:36:28,440
aren't you supposed to be in the class?

713
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:31,760
I've been feeling unwell recently.

714
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:33,000
I asked for leave with Mr. Lu.

715
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:34,110
I feel much better now.

716
00:36:34,134 --> 00:36:35,436
I'm about to go back to class.

717
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:36,600
But...

718
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,440
Hope Shujun's reading lady

719
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:39,800
will be alright.

720
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:40,890
What problem could there be?

721
00:36:41,550 --> 00:36:43,070
It's just an accident.

722
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:47,910
Mr. Yin,

723
00:36:48,670 --> 00:36:50,440
this concerns the safety of Lady Mingshu.

724
00:36:50,500 --> 00:36:51,980
It's better to investigate it clearly.

725
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:55,440
Listening to what was just said,

726
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:56,130
the incident

727
00:36:56,154 --> 00:36:57,826
seems to be related to Lady Shujun.

728
00:36:58,550 --> 00:37:00,550
I have come at the command of Noble Consort

729
00:37:00,550 --> 00:37:02,150
for the purpose of the marriage alliance.

730
00:37:02,280 --> 00:37:04,590
If this matter truly involves Lady Shujun,

731
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,550
it is imperative to investigate it clearly,

732
00:37:06,760 --> 00:37:08,480
to avoid affecting important affairs.

733
00:37:08,920 --> 00:37:10,930
I hope you will handle this matter

734
00:37:10,954 --> 00:37:12,166
with caution.

735
00:37:12,590 --> 00:37:13,440
Sure.

736
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:14,680
Noble Eunuch,

737
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,960
you take it seriously.

738
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:17,880
It's just a misunderstanding.

739
00:37:18,800 --> 00:37:20,150
But please rest assured,

740
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,050
I will make sure

741
00:37:21,174 --> 00:37:22,774
to get to the bottom of this matter,

742
00:37:23,150 --> 00:37:24,840
not to put you in a difficult position.

743
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:26,590
Since that's the case,

744
00:37:26,960 --> 00:37:28,190
I will not disturb you

745
00:37:28,190 --> 00:37:29,800
taking care of household affairs.

746
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:31,760
Goodbye.

747
00:37:36,990 --> 00:37:37,860
Yue'er,

748
00:37:37,880 --> 00:37:39,880
go invite a doctor for Lady Mingshu.

749
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:40,760
Take good care of her.

750
00:37:41,070 --> 00:37:41,910
Yes.

751
00:38:26,630 --> 00:38:27,470
You're awake.

752
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:34,480
Brother, when I fell into the water,

753
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,360
I remembered some things.

754
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,590
Maybe it was something from the past.

755
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:40,110
The past?

756
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,440
What is it?

757
00:38:44,070 --> 00:38:45,110
It's...

758
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:50,960
It seems like you saved me.

759
00:38:54,550 --> 00:38:57,030
I can't remember the specifics.

760
00:38:57,550 --> 00:38:59,110
It's okay. Don't think about it for now.

761
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:01,280
Have some ginger tea to warm your body.

762
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,550
Here.

763
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:06,510
Thank you.

764
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:13,730
I originally thought

765
00:39:13,754 --> 00:39:15,526
the Yin Family just had a lot of troubles.

766
00:39:15,850 --> 00:39:17,580
If I had known you nearly risked your life,

767
00:39:17,630 --> 00:39:18,600
I would never agree

768
00:39:18,620 --> 00:39:19,890
to keep you in the Yin Residence.

769
00:39:20,150 --> 00:39:22,150
I just got distracted for a moment,

770
00:39:22,150 --> 00:39:24,360
so I slipped into the lake.

771
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:26,590
I promise this won't happen again.

772
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:29,960
You still think of it as an accident?

773
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:31,720
The bridge surface

774
00:39:32,230 --> 00:39:33,550
was splashed with tung oil.

775
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:35,960
Tung oil is a lubricant.

776
00:39:36,510 --> 00:39:37,870
If someone accidentally spilled it,

777
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:39,230
it will definitely be reported

778
00:39:39,254 --> 00:39:40,406
and a notice will be posted

779
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:41,760
to eliminate hidden dangers.

780
00:39:42,150 --> 00:39:43,630
You mean

781
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:46,030
someone deliberately set me up?

782
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:50,580
Now that it has come to this,

783
00:39:50,660 --> 00:39:51,980
I will no longer hide it from you.

784
00:39:52,400 --> 00:39:53,800
The purpose of my visit here

785
00:39:53,800 --> 00:39:55,440
is to investigate Lady Shujun's character.

786
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:58,060
She will be questioned by Censor Yin shortly.

787
00:39:58,700 --> 00:40:00,210
If this matter is indeed caused by her,

788
00:40:01,400 --> 00:40:02,480
I must report to Prince Rui

789
00:40:02,860 --> 00:40:03,860
to dissolve the marriage.

790
00:40:04,150 --> 00:40:05,230
But I don't think it's her.

791
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,920
Today is the day she meets Noble Eunuch.

792
00:40:08,070 --> 00:40:09,880
This concerns the reputation of the family.

793
00:40:10,230 --> 00:40:11,880
How could she not understand it?

794
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,240
It's really not me.

795
00:40:19,590 --> 00:40:20,710
That reading lady

796
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:22,360
fell into water due to tung oil.

797
00:40:22,880 --> 00:40:24,010
Your mother sent someone

798
00:40:24,134 --> 00:40:25,336
to investigate each courtyard.

799
00:40:25,960 --> 00:40:28,260
Only the tung oil in your uncle's house

800
00:40:28,260 --> 00:40:29,300
is missing.

801
00:40:30,050 --> 00:40:31,440
His courtyard is short of tung oil.

802
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,740
What does it have to do with me?

803
00:40:32,880 --> 00:40:35,190
Before the incident, only Shuangyan

804
00:40:35,190 --> 00:40:36,280
has been to his courtyard.

805
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:38,480
In the entire residence, only you

806
00:40:38,480 --> 00:40:40,480
regard the reading lady as an eyesore.

807
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:41,800
Besides you, who else could it be?

808
00:40:42,510 --> 00:40:44,030
You are preconsciously judging me.

809
00:40:44,220 --> 00:40:45,570
You said it's me without checking.

810
00:40:46,100 --> 00:40:47,190
This matter is not my doing.

811
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:48,550
I will absolutely not admit to it.

812
00:40:48,920 --> 00:40:49,760
You...!

813
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:53,680
Shujun,

814
00:40:53,960 --> 00:40:54,730
are you unwilling

815
00:40:54,754 --> 00:40:56,066
to marry into the royal family?

816
00:40:56,590 --> 00:40:58,590
So you deliberately caused this trouble.

817
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:00,510
I already said it's not me.

818
00:41:00,510 --> 00:41:01,960
Why don't you believe me?

819
00:41:02,920 --> 00:41:04,800
How can I trust you?

820
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:06,710
When the rumors first started,

821
00:41:06,880 --> 00:41:07,960
I specifically investigated

822
00:41:07,984 --> 00:41:08,756
to clear your name.

823
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:12,110
But the result really disappointed me.

824
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:15,800
How did you become like this?

825
00:41:20,630 --> 00:41:21,760
Master, Madam,

826
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:23,320
please allow me

827
00:41:23,590 --> 00:41:24,710
to say a few words.

828
00:41:25,110 --> 00:41:25,950
Go ahead.

829
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,360
May I ask

830
00:41:27,860 --> 00:41:29,380
if anyone has seen with their own eyes

831
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:30,470
Shuangyan took tung oil

832
00:41:30,494 --> 00:41:31,486
from the Third Master?

833
00:41:32,510 --> 00:41:33,360
No one.

834
00:41:33,760 --> 00:41:34,600
I believe,

835
00:41:34,880 --> 00:41:36,440
catch the thief with the stolen goods.

836
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:39,590
Shuangyan just went there once.

837
00:41:39,700 --> 00:41:41,170
Whether she really took the tung oil,

838
00:41:41,170 --> 00:41:42,710
neither physical evidence nor witness.

839
00:41:43,670 --> 00:41:44,510
If you want to check,

840
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:46,070
no one can escape from it.

841
00:41:46,550 --> 00:41:48,360
We cannot let bad people go,

842
00:41:48,480 --> 00:41:49,800
nor can we wrong good people.

843
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:02,440
Master, Madam,

844
00:42:02,630 --> 00:42:04,630
the tung oil barrel has been found.

845
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:06,190
Where was it found?

846
00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:07,550
It is

847
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:10,030
found in Lady Shujun's courtyard.

848
00:42:12,760 --> 00:42:13,760
How could it be?

849
00:42:14,320 --> 00:42:15,160
You troublemaker!

850
00:42:17,440 --> 00:42:18,670
Now the proof is conclusive.

851
00:42:18,880 --> 00:42:20,150
What else do you have to say?

